Read AGENTS.md for full project guidelines. Key rules:

- Tauri v2 (Rust) + React 18 + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind CSS v4
- Zero network egress from the desktop app
- Don't use enigo on macOS — use pbcopy + osascript for paste
- Don't call AppKit from background threads — use run_on_main_thread
- Don't resize NSPanel dynamically — handle visual changes in CSS/motion
- Widget (widget.tsx) is a separate webview — no shared React state with main window
- Use motion/react for animations, inline styles for custom UI
- cocoa crate deprecation warnings are expected — don't try to fix
- Stage specific files when committing, never git add -A
- No Co-Authored-By lines in commits
